#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>N</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Next Level</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>N</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>अग्रे स्तरः</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Load the next level."
msgstr "अग्रिमस्तरं लोड् कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Previous Level</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>पूर्वस्तरः</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go back to the previous level."
msgstr "पूर्वस्तरं प्रति गच्छन्तु।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Esc;</shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Restart "
"Level</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Esc;</shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>स्तरं पुनः आरभत</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restart the current level."
msgstr "वर्तमानस्तरं पुनः आरभत।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Level Collection</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guisubmenu>स्तरसङ्ग्रह</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>A submenu to switch to a different set of levels.</action> "
"&skladnik; comes with several level sets, and you can load more that you can "
"find on the internet."
msgstr ""
"<action>स्तरस्य भिन्नसमूहं प्रति स्विच् कर्तुं उपमेनू।</action> &skladnik; अनेकस्तरसमूहैः सह "
"आगच्छति, अपि च भवन्तः अधिकं लोड् कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति यत् भवन्तः अन्तर्जालस्य उपरि प्राप्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पूर्ववत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo the last move."
msgstr "अन्तिमं चालनं पूर्ववत् कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पुनः कुरुत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Redo the last move you undid with the menu item above."
msgstr "उपरि मेनू-वस्तुना भवता अकृतं अन्तिमं चालनं पुनः कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>प्रश्न</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>निवृत्तं</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Exit</action> &skladnik;."
msgstr "<action>निर्गम</action> &skladnik;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Animation Menu"
msgstr "एनिमेशन मेनू इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu offers menu items with check boxes that allow you to specify the "
"speed to which the movement replay animations are shown at."
msgstr ""
"एतत् मेन्यू चेक् बॉक्स्-सहितं मेनू-वस्तूनि प्रदाति यत् भवन्तः गति-पुनः-प्ले एनिमेशन्स् यस्मिन् वेगे "
"दर्शिताः इति निर्दिष्टुं शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Animation</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Slow</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>एनिमेशन</guimenu> <guisubmenu>मन्द</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show replay animations at a slow pace."
msgstr "मन्दगत्या पुनः प्ले एनिमेशनं दर्शयतु।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Animation</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Medium</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>एनिमेशन</guimenu> <guisubmenu>मध्यम</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default setting, and <action>shows replay animations at a "
"slightly faster pace</action>."
msgstr ""
"एतत् पूर्वनिर्धारितं सेटिङ्ग् अस्ति, तथा च <action>किञ्चित् द्रुततरगत्या पुनः प्ले एनिमेशनं "
"दर्शयति</action> ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Animation</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Fast</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>एनिमेशन</guimenu> <guisubmenu>द्रुत</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show replay animations at the fastest pace."
msgstr "द्रुततमगत्या पुनः प्ले एनिमेशनं दर्शयतु।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Animation</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Off</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>एनिमेशन</guimenu> <guisubmenu>निष्क्रान्त</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not animate replay animations."
msgstr "पुनः प्ले एनिमेशनं न सजीवं कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Bookmarks Menu"
msgstr "बुकमार्क मेनू इति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Set Bookmark</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guimenu> <guisubmenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि सेट् कुर्वन्तु</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skladnik; allows you to <action>set bookmarks with a level at a particular "
"state.</action> You might use this to save yourself repeating the same "
"initial steps in a level."
msgstr ""
"&स्क्लद्निक; भवन्तं <action>एकस्मिन् विशेषे अवस्थायां स्तरेन सह पुस्तकचिह्नानि सेट् कर्तुं शक्नोति "
"।</action> भवान् एतत् उपयोक्तुं शक्नोति यत् भवान् कस्मिन् अपि स्तरे समानानि "
"प्रारम्भिकपदानि पुनरावृत्तिं कृत्वा स्वयमेव रक्षितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can have up to ten bookmarks at a time, and access them via the "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap><replaceable>X</replaceable></"
"keycap></keycombo> shortcut, where <replaceable>X</replaceable> is any digit "
"between 0 and 9."
msgstr ""
"भवान् एकस्मिन् समये दश पुस्तकचिह्नानि यावत् भवितुं शक्नोति, तथा च <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap><replaceable>X</replaceable></keycap></keycombo> "
"शॉर्टकट् मार्गेण तान् अभिगन्तुं शक्नोति, यत्र <replaceable >X</replaceable> इति 0 तः 9 "
"पर्यन्तं कोऽपि अङ्कः ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Go to Bookmark</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guimenu> <guisubmenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guisubmenu> इति गच्छन्तु"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jump to a state you have previously saved as a bookmark."
msgstr "पूर्वं भवता बुकमार्करूपेण रक्षितां अवस्थां प्रति कूदन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "सहायता मेनू"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skladnik; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu item, for more "
"information read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&स्क्लद्निक; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> मेनू-वस्तु, अधिकसूचनार्थं &kde; "
"मौलिकता।"

